ाः","trans":"\"You have secured boons of immunity against death at the hand s of strong and mighty and powerful valour, like gods, Danavas, Yakshas and human beings. The Vanaras, Bears and monkeys with dark faces are coming here now thundering.\"","words":[{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"देवदानवयक्षेभ्यः","m":"Devas, Danavas and Yakshas"},{"d":"वरः","m":"boons"},{"d":"गृहीतः","m":"obtained"},{"d":"बलवन्तः","m":"strong"},{"d":"दृढविक्रमाः","m":"powerful valour"},{"d":"महाबलाः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"मनुष्याः","m":"human beings"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"ऋक्षाः","m":"Bears"},{"d":"गोलाङ्गूलाः","m":"monkeys with dark face"},{"d":"इह","m":"now"},{"d":"आगम्य","m":"come here"},{"d":"गर्जन्ती","m":"thundering."}]},{"v":25,"dev":"उत्पातान्विविधान्दृष्टवाघोरन्बहुविधांस्तथा ।विनाशमनुपश्यामिसर्वेषांरक्षसामहम्","trans":"\"Beholding different dreadful ones rising up in various directions, I foresee destruction of all Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"विविधान्","m":"different"},{"d":"उत्पातान्","m":"rising up"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"बहुविधान्","m":"in various ways"},{"d":"घोरान्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"सर्वेषाम्","m":"all"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"विनाशम्","m":"destruction"},{"d":"अनुपश्यामि","m":"foresee."}]},{"v":26,"dev":"खराभिस्न्तिताघोरामेघाःप्रतिभयङ्कराः ।शोणितेनाभिवर्षन्तिलङ्कामुष्णेनसर्वतः","trans":"\"Formidable clouds are emitting hot and most frightening thunder drenched by rain of blood all over Lanka.\"","words":[{"d":"खराभिस्न्तिताः","m":"emitting hot thunder"},{"d":"घोराः","m":"formidable"},{"d":"प्रतिभयङ्कराः","m":"very frightening"},{"d":"मेघाः","m":"clouds"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"सर्वतः","m":"all over"},{"d":"उष्णेन","m":"by the heat"},{"d":"शोणितेन","m":"by blood"},{"d":"अभिवर्षन्ति","m":"raining."}]},{"v":27,"dev":"रुदतांवाहनानांचप्रपवन्त्यौस्रबिन्दवः ।ध्वजाध्वस्ताविवर्णाश्चनप्रभान्तियथापुरम्","trans":"\"With tear drops falling from the eyes of weeping horses and elephant